## Key Rules

1. **Keep PRDs focused** - One feature at a time
2. **Be specific** - Vague requirements lead to wrong implementation
3. **Define data model** - Critical for database setup
4. **List all endpoints** - Backend needs clear API definition
5. **Name UI components** - Frontend needs component list
6. **Set boundaries** - Out of scope prevents feature creep
7. **Make success criteria testable** - Clear done definition

